{"tid":2409894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［劣根性］ 支那翁抱大疊人民幣 細路要叩頭逗利是","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T09:31:51.000Z","uid":374134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43ddd94619e2d26066c4245619dfc3cbf459a25d","tid":2409894,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp0EbP5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp0EbP5.jpg&h=4171d1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新年派利是是傳統習俗，網上流傳一段短片，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"gold\">河南一名伯伯向孫兒派一大疊利是，期間孫兒下跪並磕頭，又講祝賀說話，引起討論。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n片段見到伯伯坐在椅子上準備給孫仔派利是，<strong>當時伯伯抱著一大疊「鈔票山」，粗略估超過10萬元人民幣</strong>。<span class=\"red\">孫仔見狀下跪磕頭，又講祝賀說話</span>，<strong>伯伯其後將一疊又一疊的人民幣派給孫仔</strong>，逗得眾人哈哈大笑。<br />\n<br />\n事實<strong>這疊鈔票並非孩子的利是，而是準備付給建築商的「工程費」</strong>，<span class=\"green\">只是拿出來當道具，跟孩子玩一下，之後就會把錢繳出去</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fxhnT3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfxhnT3A.jpg&h=afde6030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網民質疑給予小朋友錯誤訊息，「這是在教導孩子跪下磕頭就有錢拿嗎？」，亦有網民表示羨慕，「缺孫子嗎」、「過年逗大家開心」。"},{"pid":"f6552c77f9a11e2e5390170f6b6ea39610d17891","tid":2409894,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1999440/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E7%BF%81%E6%8A%B1%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%8A%E9%8A%80%E7%B4%99-%E5%AD%AB%E4%BB%94%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%AA%E7%A3%95%E9%A0%AD-%E9%80%97%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF-%E6%83%B9%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9b7af67a79f2e31b374b208121efa9ba31224b1b","tid":2409894,"uid":373119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"邊到有得跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb8426e310de06abf8bf8f43320f976b4df8c4a","tid":2409894,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7af67a79f2e31b374b208121efa9ba31224b1b","tid":2409894,"uid":373119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"邊到有得跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"中國河南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44aa53889ee3fb681c3fe000862d421a0f27fd0","tid":2409894,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"土下座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4af7365d13954225754ffdbcd58ec81364d9b","tid":2409894,"uid":103916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"偷、呃、拐、騙，支那國技術。"},{"pid":"afa9f2afcab4d4944895afec902cca55dc5061a2","tid":2409894,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"工程費畀現金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n厲害了我的國"}]}